        {
          "reviewTitle": "Pretty and smelly",
          "reviewText": "Overall this is a nice foundation. I used the Instagram filter to find my shade and it is the perfect color. It is very light and had pretty decent cover as well. However I don\u2019t think I\u2019ll be buying it again because of the smell. I was very surprised to find fragrance on the ingredients list considering it\u2019s supposed to be so high tech and good for your skin. It\u2019s a very sharp perfume smell that\u2019s very strong. If they stopped putting perfume in it I would absolutely buy it again though.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2025",
